description: Detroit Mini Donut is brought to you by Karen Hudson and Karla Willis, two driven ladies with a mission to help restore the city of Detroit one delicious mini donut at a time. This truck is exclusively run by young inner city women who are on their path toward success. Once you try a bite of any of these sweet treats on the streets, you’ll have no doubt that this talented team has what it takes. You’ll also find refreshing Motor City Lemonade and authentic Italian Ice, so be sure to come delight in some Detroit Mini Donuts soon!!
name: Detroit Mini Donut
